OL,3,COfgem: Debt relief scheme would add #6
OL,4,Cto energy bills
OL,6,FA senior energy industry official has
OL,7,Ftold ITV News that its new debt plan
OL,8,Fwill add #6 to a typical energy bill
OL,9,Fper year.
OL,11,FThe Ofgem spokesperson has also
OL,12,Fconfirmed that the scheme could also
OL,13,Fbe doubled in size - eventually
OL,14,Fcosting up to #1 billion and wiping
OL,15,Foff debts for 2.3 million customers.
OL,17,FThe energy regulator Ofgem is planning
OL,18,Fa scheme to write-off energy debts for
OL,19,Faround 195,000 customers who build up
OL,20,Farrears during the period when prices
OL,21,Fpeaked.
