OL,3,COfgem: Debt relief scheme would add #6
OL,4,Cto energy bills
OL,6,FThe plan, due to start early next
OL,7,Fyear, would be funded by customers -
OL,8,Fnot by the energy industry.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News, Charlotte Friel,
OL,11,FDirector for Retail Pricing at Ofgem,
OL,12,Fconfirmed that the scheme would add
OL,13,F50p a month to an average bill.
OL,15,FThe energy regulator says that if
OL,16,Fnothing was done about the energy debt
OL,17,Fmountain, now standing at #4.4
OL,18,Fbillion, customers would end up paying
OL,19,Fmore to deal with the arrears.
