OL,3,COfgem: Debt relief scheme would add #6
OL,4,Cto energy bills
OL,6,FThe planned debt write-off scheme is
OL,7,Fonly phase one of what could be a much
OL,8,Fbigger scheme - which could expand to
OL,9,Fdeal with up to #1 billion in energy
OL,10,Fdebt. It's estimated that #1.9 billion
OL,11,Fin arrears built up in the so-called
OL,12,F"energy crisis" after the invasion of
OL,13,FUkraine.
OL,15,FThe proposed debt relief scheme
OL,16,Finitially aims to cut #500m from
OL,17,Farrears, helping households who are on
OL,18,Fmeans tested benefits.
