OL,3,COfgem: Debt relief scheme would add #6
OL,4,Cto energy bills
OL,6,FTo be eligible, customers must have
OL,7,Fmore than #100 of debt built up
OL,8,Fbetween April 2022 - and March 2024,
OL,9,Fwhen energy prices peaked.
OL,11,FThey will be identified automatically
OL,12,Fand contacted by suppliers.
